Description: Thermalright LCD/LED Control Center for Linux
 Linux implementation of the Thermalright LCD Control Center (TRCC).
 Controls LCD displays and LED segment displays on Thermalright CPU coolers
 and AIO liquid coolers.
 .
 Requires python3-pyside6 in apt — suitable for Debian 13+ and distros
 that package PySide6 as a system package. For Ubuntu 24.04 use the
 legacy .deb package instead.
 .
 Features:
  - GUI (PySide6) with full Windows TRCC feature parity
  - CLI (Typer) with 50+ commands
  - REST API (FastAPI) with 49 endpoints
  - Theme management, video playback, LED RGB effects
  - Supports SCSI, HID, Bulk, and LY USB protocols
